title: (1965) - Dr Who and the Daleks (Peter Cushing).avi
description:
For all of you classic Doctor Who fans that have downloaded all 26 years worth of the Doctor, I finally found the one broadcast that has alluded me for a long time. Back in 1965, the BBC commissioned a Doctor Who movie starring Peter Cushing. Okay, the movie was terribly done. It even lacked the defining Doctor musical theme, but one cannot consider the collection complete without it.

Enjoy and pass it around to the rest of the Whovian community.

BNaron
